
usage: acct [options]
   -n    add a new player (info file on stdin)
   -a    email the new player a short ACK
   -l n  log credit/debit of n (give p and y)
   -t    charge a turn (give p and y)
   -i      this is an idle turn (reduced rate)
   -p n  player account to credit/debit to
   -y n  comment for credit/debit
   -s n  account summary, last n log entries
   -m    list accounts at or below zero
   -c       ... only if they pay by credit card
   -f    list players with free turns
   -A    list all accounts
   -d    delete player account



no arena turn will be run for which funds are not available

acct -A -N [ -p player ]		Add new Arena player
					accept info on stdin
					allocate id if -p not given
					return id unconditionally on stdout

acct -A -T x -p player			Can an Arena turn costing X be run?
acct -A -t x -p player -y comment	Charge an Arena turn costing X
acct -A -p player -s 4			Arena account summary
acct -A -p player -d			Delete Arena player

new arena player


